      <title>《魔法师之夜》全成就攻略与游玩心得</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/2025-10-14-%E9%AD%94%E6%B3%95%E5%B8%88%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%9C%E5%85%A8%E6%88%90%E5%B0%B1%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5%E4%B8%8E%E6%B8%B8%E7%8E%A9%E5%BF%83%E5%BE%97/</link>
